<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>게시글 상세보기</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.0.min.js"></script>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f9;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 15px;
            font-size: 24px;
        }

        .container {
            width: 80%;
            margin: 40px auto;
            background-color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .post-title {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .post-date {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #888;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .post-content {
            font-size: 18px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .comment-section {
            margin-top: 40px;
        }

        .comment-header {
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .comment-list {
            list-style-type: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .comment-list li {
            padding: 15px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
        }

        .comment-list .comment-author {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #4CAF50;
        }

        .comment-list .comment-date {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #888;
        }

        .comment-list .comment-content {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .add-post {
            padding: 6px 12px;
            background-color: red;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .comment-form {
            margin-top: 40px;
        }

        .comment-form input {
            width: 15%;
            padding: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 16px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
        }

        .comment-form textarea {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px;
            font-size: 16px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 5px;
            height: 100px;
            font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
        }

        .comment-form button {
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .comment-form button:hover {
            background-color: #45a049;
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            position: fixed;
            width: 100%;
            bottom: 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
    게시글 상세보기
</header>

<div class="container">
    <div class="post-title">{{board.title}}</div>
    <div class="post-date">{{board.createDate}}</div>
    <div class="post-content">
        <p>{{board.content}}</p>
    </div>
</div>

<footer>
    © 2025 양정인력개발센터 - 모든 권리 보유
</footer>


</body>
</html>
